### ========================================
### T3 - URL Shortener API
### ========================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@code = abc123

### ----------------------------------------
### GET / - Información del API
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ----------------------------------------
### POST /shorten - Crear URL corta
### ----------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.google.com"
}

### ----------------------------------------
### GET /:code - Redirigir a URL original
### (Usa el código devuelto por POST /shorten)
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{code}}

### ----------------------------------------
### GET /stats/:code - Estadísticas de URL
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats/{{code}}

### ----------------------------------------
### GET /api/urls - Listar todas las URLs
### ----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/urls

### ----------------------------------------
### DELETE /api/urls/:code - Eliminar URL
### ----------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/urls/{{code}}

### ========================================
### Casos de prueba adicionales
### ========================================

### POST /shorten - URL inválida (sin protocolo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "www.google.com"
}

### POST /shorten - Sin URL (campo vacío)
POST {{baseUrl}}/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": ""
}

### POST /shorten - Body vacío
POST {{baseUrl}}/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### GET /stats/:code - Código inexistente
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats/noexiste

### DELETE /api/urls/:code - Código inexistente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/urls/noexiste

### GET /:code - Código inexistente (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/noexiste

### GET - Ruta no encontrada (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ruta/que/no/existe
